<L>__{interior de lessepses' house. viola's bedroom. night.}
<A>__{the nurse is helping viola into her party dress.}
<C>__{nurse}
<D>__{your mother, and your father}
<C>__{viola}
<P>__{(gaily)}
<D>__{from tomorrow, away in the country for three weeks! is master shakespeare not handsome?}
<C>__{nurse}
<D>__{he looks well enough for a mountebank.}
<C>__{viola}
<D>__{oh, nurse! he would give thomas kent the life of viola de lesseps's dreaming.}
<C>__{nurse}
<P>__{(firmly)}
<D>__{my lady, this play will end badly. i will tell.}
<C>__{viola}
<P>__{(twice as firmly)}
<D>__{you will not tell. as you love me and as i love you, you will bind my breast and buy me a boy's wig!}
